{"tid":233512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(無圖) 行李壞左 保養期內都整/換唔番個...求教","createTime":"2017-05-07T15:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T19:20:36.000Z","uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04ed575e5890531b55ebe4c5810f7a316989b5c2","tid":233512,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"係delsey買左個行李 <br />\n年頭壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去太古delsey問下點樣整番<br />\n職員話已經整唔番 可以換一個同等價錢同款既行李比我....之後等左成3個月..打佢地店既電話無人聽...落去追問就話搵唔到相關既行李款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大間公司...一個差唔多款既都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我其實唔多信<br />\n<br />\n但我9月想去台灣旅行...唔想再用行李袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔捨得買個新既行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以點...巴絲請救...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/230124_732fb19b9c41db715c3817d4f99e3331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F230124_732fb19b9c41db715c3817d4f99e3331.jpg&h=f5b7e16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OS2gYV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OS2gYV.jpg&h=385953ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8423f3bdb543cf3717eab787855e58e88c4f9c","tid":233512,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"send去消費者委員會幫你搞啦"},{"pid":"09c0a5ab12946b9334f460e2715f6d7f3e84e79d","tid":233512,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>s