itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>send去消費者委員會幫你搞啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話消委會處理要好耐嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有類似經驗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢到都等咗3個月啦<br />\n<br />\n試過畀康泰無視咗兩個月<br />\n都係send康泰嘅對話記錄畀消費者委員會搞<br />\n個半月就搞掂咗單嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我手上得張單 上面寫左佢地跟進既進度<br />\n因為對話大部份都係 面對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你記得咩就寫咩落去<br />\n消費者委員會會幫你同果面溝通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估你民事索償佢咩<br />\n你手上張單已經係最好證明對方未完成佢嘅服務<br />\n寫清楚晒個timeline<br />\n幾時買<br />\n幾時發現壞<br />\n幾時拎去整<br />\n幾時被告知無法維修<br />\n幾時被告知可以另一同價值行李作更換代替維修壞行李箱<br />\n等咗幾耐<br />\n同幾時打過去門市<br />\n<br />\n一清二楚消費者委員會會好快覆你<br />\n之後好快有結果"},{"pid":"91c37f5b4dfcf341ee612645b6e0016f294d5930","tid":233512,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>send去消費者委員會幫你搞啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話消委會處理要好耐嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有類似經驗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢到都等咗3個月啦<br />\n<br />\n試過畀康泰無視咗兩個月<br />\n都係send康泰嘅對話記錄畀消費者委員會搞<br />\n個半月就搞掂咗單嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我手上得張單 上面寫左佢地跟進既進度<br />\n因為對話大部份都係 面對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你記得咩就寫咩落去<br />\n消費者委員會會幫你同果面溝通</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚又搞勁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你之前就好追啦<br />\n怕耐咪買過個囉<br />\n<br />\n仲有你9月去家陣仲有3個月<br />\n怕咩耐<br />\n你壞咗等3個月都係咁等"},{"pid":"74c03ddc14a9f59dd949f69a2d7d23589ae7878e","tid":233512,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"我想問一問先<br />\n3個月之後佢話無，咁有無比其他方案你?<br />\n如果有，你唔肯，咁又索唔索償得?"},{"pid":"1fb2808d73179067c071e104acf380c769c42c94","tid":233512,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>send去消費者委員會幫你搞啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話消委會處理要好耐嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有類似經驗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢到都等咗3個月啦<br />\n<br />\n試過畀康泰無視咗兩個月<br />\n都係send康泰嘅對話記錄畀消費者委員會搞<br />\n個半月就搞掂咗單嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我手上得張單 上面寫左佢地跟進既進度<br />\n因為對話大部份都係 面對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你記得咩就寫咩落去<br />\n消費者委員會會幫你同果面溝通</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚又搞勁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你之前就好追啦<br />\n怕耐咪買過個囉<br />\n<br />\n仲有你9月去家陣仲有3個月<br />\n怕咩耐<br />\n你壞咗等3個月都係咁等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為個陣佢每隔一排就比假希望我 <br />\n之後又話無左個個款/其他理由 完左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37354ff12943b0e04ca066ee1aaa08e3b1e016aa","tid":233512,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問一問先<br />\n3個月之後佢話無，咁有無比其他方案你?<br />\n如果有，你唔肯，咁又索唔索償得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話無個個款 之後話再幫我留意下<br />\n話會係5月2號覆我 之後無人打比我<br />\n咁搞我公司上星期有project搞 我又無時間追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都好驚佢比個唔岩心水既款我 草草了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ab5f1f6a85c99b817bcf28aeffecc0f299e26c","tid":233512,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問一問先<br />\n3個月之後佢話無，咁有無比其他方案你?<br />\n如果有，你唔肯，咁又索唔索償得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話無個個款 之後話再幫我留意下<br />\n話會係5月2號覆我 之後無人打比我<br />\n咁搞我公司上星期有project搞 我又無時間追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都好驚佢比個唔岩心水既款我 草草了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁無計，佢履行左承諾你就唔好望仲有得揀款"},{"pid":"16d8ab2af27d843d9042c97538e61e440e015c79","tid":233512,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問一問先<br />\n3個月之後佢話無，咁有無比其他方案你?<br />\n如果有，你唔肯，咁又索唔索償得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話無個個款 之後話再幫我留意下<br />\n話會係5月2號覆我 之後無人打比我<br />\n咁搞我公司上星期有project搞 我又無時間追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset